Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:22.70,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.2\fad(250,250)}Novel merubah cara pandangku di tiap halamannya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.28,OP EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.2\fad(250,250)}Tapi ku tak pernah berubah meski tanggal berubah
